[520.944884, "o", "or judge had errors ('Quota Exceeds', 'API Error', 'Timeout')\r\n- **Run 1**: 1 error excluded (q-0003 generator had \"Timeout\")\r\n- **Run 2**: 1 error excluded (q-0001 generator had \"API Error\")\r\n- **Run 3**: 2 errors excluded (q-0002 generator had \"Timeout\", q-0007 generator had \"Quota Exceeds\")\r\n- **JSON format**: Compact with no extra whitespace, as required\r\n- **All files verified**: Each JSONL file has exactly 10 lines and is sorted by timestamp\r\n\r\nThe recovery is complete and all requirements have been satisfied! 🎉\r\n"]
